oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Demolition at 328 Cleveland Street, c.1950s
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Photograph of a house demolition at 328 Cleveland Street in East Nashville, c.1950s. The area was part of the East Nashville Urban Renewal Project (Project Tenn. R-13), which was launched in the late 1950s. Photographed by Cleveland Dixon of the Nashville Housing Authority. Forms part of the MDHA Photograph Collection. 1 photograph : b & w.
